---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import site from '../data/site.json';
---

<Layout title="Music - Claire Zhang" description="Guzheng performances and musical exploration." path="music">
	<div class="mt-12 md:mt-24 mb-16 max-w-3xl">
		<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-light mb-6">Music & Performance</h1>
		<p class="text-[#6f6963] leading-relaxed text-lg mb-8">
			The Guzheng (古筝) is not merely an instrument; it is a canvas of sound. With years of practice and performance, I explore the profound resonance of traditional Chinese music while seeking contemporary interpretations. The discipline of music informs my visual design—both require rhythm, tension, and the beauty of negative space.
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="space-y-24 mb-24">
		{site.performances.map((perf) => (
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
				<div class="md:col-span-8 bg-[#EDE8E1] aspect-video relative group overflow-hidden">
					<iframe
						src={perf.videoUrl}
						title={perf.title}
						class="w-full h-full"
						allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
						allowfullscreen
					></iframe>
				</div>
				<div class="md:col-span-4">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-2">{perf.title}</h3>
					<div class="flex flex-col text-xs text-[#A9A39A] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] space-y-2 mb-4 font-sans">
						<span>{perf.date}</span>
						<span>{perf.location}</span>
						<span>{perf.piece} · {perf.duration}</span>
					</div>
					<p class="text-[#6f6963] font-light text-sm">A short reflection on the piece and its emotional core, to be replaced with her own interpretation.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		))}
	</div>
</Layout>